Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:24:00.66,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}分からないままに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:05.79,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}怖がってた　後ろの自分が現実を
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:11.51,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:16.84,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:21.52,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ここはきっと儚い心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.52,0:24:24.23,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:24.85,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢で！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:28.65,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高く飛んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:34.95,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}体はどんな不安まとっても振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:39.37,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}守る　小さな思い
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.37,0:24:43.54,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}広がりだして　気づく　弱い私
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:47.37,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君がいれば　暗い世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.37,0:24:50.29,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.88,0:24:55.97,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}長い夢見る心は　そう　永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.47,0:25:00.14,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fnArial}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.18,0:25:05.43,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\fnArial}I give everything I have
Comment: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OPCH
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:54.74,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}面對過去懦弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:24:00.66,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}即使仍是懵懵懂懂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:11.51,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}害怕如今的自己 身後的映出的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:16.84,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}萬物繪出的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:21.52,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}卻是顆脆弱無比的心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.52,0:24:24.23,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}以此為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:24.85,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在夢想中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:28.65,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}展翅高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.65,0:24:34.95,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不管身體為多少不安鎖住 都將其拂去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:39.37,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}守住那小小的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.37,0:24:43.54,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}察覺到不斷蔓延的 羸弱的我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:50.29,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}若此世有你 堙黯的世界裡我也能堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.88,0:24:55.97,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}在無盡的夢裡 我心永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.47,0:25:00.14,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}與君相伴 直至天荒地老
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.18,0:25:05.43,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我將為你 獻出我的所有
