Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:36.87,OP2-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\blur4\fad(150,200)}眼前的這片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:39.69,OP2-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\blur4\fad(150,200)}便能超越過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:44.71,OP2-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord3\blur4\fad(150,200)}便能朝未來的方向
